Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:07.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,明灭之地 未生时 尚存点滴光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:09.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,请多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢 也多谢大家暗中相助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:17.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不足挂齿 事到如今也只能信任他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:18.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:23.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,飘摆摇曳 若星火 闪烁耀人心房
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:30.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是说石像鬼小队全员参加咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:35.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我们也都想知道皆志他们\N出生的岛屿上到底都发生过些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:36.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有神木…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是有神木的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:44.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我们还在岛上的时候是有很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:48.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有那些树的话艾米露他们复原的希望也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:54.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 明天拂晓前开始秘密行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:59.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎么去岛上呢 跟自卫队借运输机还是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:03.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然争取到很多肯在暗中帮助我们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:08.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但出动运輸机又要不惊动外人还是太困难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是有一个地方会有我们能用的飞机的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:14.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:16.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,无明领域里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:22.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们首先要赶往已经废弃的厚木基地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:34.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,萤辉隐现 何人祈愿 抱残余期望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:38.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,秣马厉兵 只待迈向彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,终于要进入无明领域了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:47.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但受到影响最大的应该是不是共联者的须崎教官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:51.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不过有你们在我相信一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:57.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 车到山前必有路
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:20.99,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}にじんでる歩道橋のらくがき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:32.21,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}置いてかれた自転車　誰かの帰りを待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:37.38,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}認めて　ただ存在を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.01,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕こそがオリジナル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.51,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}あるいはそのレプリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:46.97,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕らの証明はどこにある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:51.81,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}人類の欠点は　見えもしないくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:57.07,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}愛とか絆とか信じられること
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:01.99,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕の罪はうたがったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.16,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}差し伸べられた君の右手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.12,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}初めて見たヒカリ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:17.17,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕らは———
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:20.99,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,岁月流转　天桥涂鸦终归消散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:32.21,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,静置难安　单车默待谁人与共还
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:37.38,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,坦然直面　存在世间　身外孑然一片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.01,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,却难断　吾乃本源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.51,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,抑或水月云烟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:46.97,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,孰真孰幻　吾等安辩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:51.81,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,人心缺点难免　未曾得见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:57.07,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,爱与羁绊　却坚信依然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:01.99,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心疑难掩　吾罪何堪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.16,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,与君右手紧牵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.12,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,唯慨叹　光明初现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:17.17,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,吾等只盼……
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:36.94,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1029,1029)\pos(1354,700)}第十八话\N读岛真相
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎已经进入无明领域了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,多加小心啊 须酱 大家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 今天还真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,检查三台MA-Vess的数据嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心就通宵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:58.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,根据检查结果来看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:03.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司他们三个人都没有出现尸钢化的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你就没什么想法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:12.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司可是在无明领域里待了好几天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:18.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…这根本无关紧要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能确定其原因的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说无关紧要了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:28.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以有MA-Vess以外进入无明领域的可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:32.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪方面考虑肯定都是没有必要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这人已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:39.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我说啊 这数据我怎么想都想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:40.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来看看呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:42.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鹭沼赤司的这个共信率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:51.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,按其他数据推算应该达到上限了才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:56.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可就这么停在87％你觉得这是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 有点奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:02.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 不会是你做了什么手脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:05.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:10.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,共信率竟然突破了理论上限？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:10.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:17.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么重要的数据你不让我看到底是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:18.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:23.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我对你还抱有一个身为科学家的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可你居然背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:27.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这贱人爱咋咋地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,去把赤司叫来 现在马上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能我亲自来调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司现在不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:34.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,他去读岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:42.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？在数据上动手脚原来只是拖时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真木皆志这是想要寻回记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒是可喜可贺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是厚木基地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 视线变模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,须崎教官 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,快去跑道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 他在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那里没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是无明领域让你看到的幻影而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要输给心魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要保持清醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:32.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那个人早就不在了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有能用的飞机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:50.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,岩人你先上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:52.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 能飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚彻夜读过说明书了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,以前没飞过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是让菜鸟也能上手才叫说明书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,快坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,来夏 赤司 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:26.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是轻一点呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 别乱动呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到机关枪这么难用嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勉强自己嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:37.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:38.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:43.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这几天没见 好像你整个人都变了似的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:52.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你们两个也变了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我有过一个未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在五年前的一场事故里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我本以为我已经走出他的阴影了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:16.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情就算你逼着自己去忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也会有零星种种难以抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆志…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是读岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目她的诞生之地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:53.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还在的时候这岛是凭着无明石大人的庇护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不为外人所见 也不存在于地图之上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,无明石？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这座岛的守护神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:04.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在骸的体内 是无明领域的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是这一切的元凶吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,神木呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这…完全没有神木的气息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:13.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,神木…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:21.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是神木吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:23.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,全都枯死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,以前在春天都会盛开得很漂亮的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那时大家还在院子里一起赏花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦 这里是门厅 然后这里是起居室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,卧室是更里面的一间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:53.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,院子对面是笹目和鸫的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三个每天都在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为岛上没有其他的小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:15.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,以前IX的旧标志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:23.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家被带到这里以后就再也没有回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你不要紧吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 别过来 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这些也不合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:14.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,再把兴奋剂量加大一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:15.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,夏入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明势头还不错的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不错 还是很顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:37.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不堪忍受实验的痛苦自寻短见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能把身体换给我多好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里竟然发生过如此惨无人道的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是看到过去发生在这里的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:03.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:23.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真想不到竟然会在这种地方见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:25.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是无人机？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要说这机体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:31.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是当初妥善封存在这岛上的最早的MA-Vess啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:36.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,装载了复制自人类的共信模块
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之就是界联系统的先祖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆志？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:50.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对你而言应该有更合适的称呼才对吧 皆志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:57.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,通过对互相的意识进行共信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不通过语言也可以进行沟通的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:14.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人 我称之为 共联者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 简直蠢到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我的假说没有错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:21.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人都具有成为共联者的潜质
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,简直浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:27.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个共信模块就是基于这个理论
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:31.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,共联者可以通过思维对机械进行控制
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可谓是革命性的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一群蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:45.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮废物竟然不能理解我崇高的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:50.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠蔑视我来维护你们那脆弱的自尊了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上难道只剩这些白痴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为这样是不对的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:06.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你的研究如果能顺利进行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不通过语言 任何人之间也都可以正确地交流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:13.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:15.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫真木未明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:18.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,共联者？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:24.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你的话 你是觉得哪里不对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要寻短见的念头是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:33.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对于你刚才的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有身为共联者的你的协助的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,应该一定可以实现的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那实在是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:04.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:10.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:14.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们终于点头要给这个项目拔款了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:20.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们想要的只是个思维控制界面而巳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:27.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们对人与人的思维联结还是持怀疑态度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 你一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:33.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你所投身的如此崇高的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会得到认同的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:37.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:46.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,人们一定能藉由你的力量抛开语言联结在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能再有其他共联者就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:56.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,研究要继续深入的话需要扩大样本范围啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个岛就是读岛了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:08.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那就是我出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:14.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里如你所见是个落后于时代的地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:27.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家真的都是共联者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:28.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:33.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这个岛估计到那些孩子这一代就要结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:40.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能在那之前创造出一个\N我们可以昂首挺胸生活的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:46.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是自然 我一定做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊 不要再做这样过分的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:57.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是必要的实验啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 我这就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,别来捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:06.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那痛苦就是共信的证据啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:10.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 拜你所赐研究有了长足的进展
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:13.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,快来夸奖我吧 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:16.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:20.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,共信的研究很快就要有成果了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想想你为此都干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:25.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么…不就是实验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是你的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:32.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,项目委员会可没批准你进行这么不人道的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是政界还是商界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:37.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,万一消息走漏了可是要吃不了兜着走的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是必须的实验啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且死掉的也都是自杀…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:45.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,多说无用 这里的实验设施全部要销毁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:49.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,回头我会派人来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你去收拾一下准备离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,呿 蠢货…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要管那帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,未明我们来继续实验好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,早知如此就不该带你来这岛上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了达成我的心愿你才会这样的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:12.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这说什么呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:38.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,未明…未明…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为这样是不对的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:07.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,人们一定能藉由你的力量抛开语言联结在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个共信模块就是基于这个理论
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:22.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 以后我要一直追随在那个人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是共信反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是糟糕透顶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:44.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是糟糕透顶的最佳杰作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:52.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,之后的事你应该比我更清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:57.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为了向我们复仇创造了无明领域吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:01.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:05.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 一点都不奇怪 我反倒要感谢你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:08.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜你们创造无明领域所赐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:12.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的研究又有了长足的进步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:17.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,本来计划已经被废止了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:22.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但要进入那里界联系统不可或缺那就另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:26.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是你…要不是你的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:30.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫也就不用创造出无明领域了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:36.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你们也就不会相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:40.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会有这些愤怒悲伤快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:45.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,永远那么平淡地生活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说那该多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:53.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司也会把自己那点出息都怪到哥哥头上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:55.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直对他这样怨恨下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,回去之后我就去告发你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的所作所为 你所犯下的罪业！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,罪业？何等失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那简直是功绩才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你简直是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:13.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过非常遗憾 你们是回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,全都尸钢化在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:18.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说界联系统也算堪用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:22.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还有更长远的梦想要实现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:27.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们尸钢化大概能成为不错的研究样本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底把人命当什么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:32.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,断不饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}绝不饶恕…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:48.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赐之戒缚 尽归于骸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:49.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是从哪里来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:59.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}绝不饶恕…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:08.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}绝不饶恕…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:33.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}绝不饶恕…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是无明领域吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:18.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不饶恕…绝不饶恕…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:32.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,自寻短见却还要变成怪物跑出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:34.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是蠢得无可救药啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.06,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You lose your mind, you crash
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.94,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A nervous breakdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:02.90,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You feel an urge inside, you crush
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:04.57,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no escape now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.74,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You try to change your life, you jump
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.49,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Another letdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.66,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But then you hear a voice inside
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.28,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You gotta open up your vision
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.91,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}See the life bestowed on you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:18.12,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Blinded by reality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:20.67,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Broken ideology
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.17,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Heart in captivity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.04,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.34,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Exceeding the borders within
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.92,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seize your capability
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.38,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Endless possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.76,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Find your individuality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.47,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Take pride, let the chase begin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.93,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me what direction you think I should take
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.39,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I know I'm gonna find the way』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.48,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me that this sable is for my own sake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.27,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『Hear what I've got to say』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:47.23,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me to believe the decisions you make
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.11,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I'm facing a new day』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:51.65,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So open up your blinded eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:54.12,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop living a lie and start living your life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.24,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.95,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today you're falling away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:00.83,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:03.88,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today I'm breaking away
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.06,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,失汝心志　躯形难继
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.94,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,慌乱分崩离析
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:02.90,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心潮涌动　冲荡破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:04.57,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,已是无路可退
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.74,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,逆天改命　奋力跃腾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.49,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,再落心灰意冷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.66,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,却闻心中轻语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.28,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,放眼茫然四顾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.91,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,但见尘世夺予
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:18.12,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,现实毁盲双目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:20.67,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,仅余碎裂思悟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.17,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心亦牢牢禁锢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.04,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,勿言轻弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.34,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,跨越心中束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.92,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,紧握汝力天成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.38,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,迸发无尽可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.76,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,寻汝真我个性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.47,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,昂首迈步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.93,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫要擅自定吾前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.39,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾定将自寻通途』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.48,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫言黑暗皆为吾敌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.27,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『但得静闻吾倾诉』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:47.23,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫诳吾从尔等好恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.11,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾自面崭新朝暮』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:51.65,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,故舍犹豫再开盲眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:54.12,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,挣脱谎言自立世间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.24,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.95,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,此时汝却飘然离去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:00.83,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:03.88,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,今日吾将突破禁锢
